data.title: Tom Cruise
data.meta_description: Tom Cruise - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Tom Cruise was born in 1962 and became famous in the 1980s for his role in Risky Business. In the 1990s, he became one of the world's most popular film stars. Some of his most notable films include Rain Man, Born on the Fourth of July, Jerry Maguire, and Mission: Impossible. Cruise has received critical acclaim for his roles and won several Golden Globe Awards for his acting performances.
